      <p>Let <italic>M</italic> be set of genomic marks such as histone modifications, transcription factor binding sites that are shown to be linked to several Hi-C interaction structures [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="CR5">5</xref>]. These marks are candidates to explain observed Hi-C interactions and associated biases. We define <inline-formula id="IEq4"><alternatives><tex-math id="M7">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
